======================================================================
IS H DETERMINED BY E(S)? (Additive Energy)
======================================================================

--- PART 1: FULL E -> H MAPPING ---

  p=7, m=3, 2^m = 8 orientations:
         E  count             H values   determined
        15      2                [189] YES
        19      6                [175] YES

    H is FULLY determined by E(S) at p=7

  p=11, m=5, 2^m = 32 orientations:
         E  count             H values   determined
        65      2              [95095] YES
        69     10              [92411] YES
        73     10              [93467] YES
        85     10              [93027] YES

    H is FULLY determined by E(S) at p=11

  p=13, m=6, 2^m = 64 orientations:
