       114      4            [3703011] YES
       118     24   [3683797, 3704857] NO ***
       122     12            [3669497] YES
       130     12            [3707483] YES
       146     12            [3711175] YES

    H is NOT determined by E(S) at p=13

--- PART 2: THE FUNCTION H = f(E) ---
If H is determined by E, we can write H = a_0 + a_1*E + a_2*E^2 + ...

  p=7: E -> H mapping:
    E=    15 -> H=       189
    E=    19 -> H=       175
    Slopes dH/dE: ['-3.50']

  p=11: E -> H mapping:
    E=    65 -> H=     95095
    E=    69 -> H=     92411
    E=    73 -> H=     93467
    E=    85 -> H=     93027
